  <entry>
    <title>Tomcat停止后Java进程残留问题及解决方法</title>
    <link href="https://gloamfox.github.io/shutdown-ming-ling-wu-fa-wan-quan-ting-zhi-tomcat/"/>
    <id>https://gloamfox.github.io/shutdown-ming-ling-wu-fa-wan-quan-ting-zhi-tomcat/</id>
    <published>2025-11-20T06:25:56.000Z</published>
    <updated>2026-03-19T10:41:21.716Z</updated>
    
    
      
      
        
        
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;运行shutdown.sh,tomcat停止, 但它的java进程还在, 不过状态为S(sleep), 不是运行时的R(Runnable), 如果不kill的话, 这种进程越来越多，导致JVM进程越来越多, 占据了大量的内存空间,</summary>
        
      
    
    
    
